      "index": 0,
      "text": "We've finally made it to [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLuderitz],Luderitz]], which Dr. Murad has determined might contain some indications about the true identity of the [[DM.Factions[faction_TortugaPirates],Satan's Kittens]] leader, Laura Murray. \n\nAs you may remember, there are still a lot of unanswered questions about who she is, so Doctor, please brief us on your findings.",
