    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c46ab507975629db58c7aca"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Well, If she truly is Natasha Kerensky, then this is nothing new for the Black Widow's behavior since there's already plenty of speculation about the Periphery origin of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreWolfsDragoons],Wolf's Dragoons]]. \n\nIf they're interested in this area, then that would be news that the Dragoon leadership might want to keep hidden from the rest of the Inner Sphere. Thus you have a possible reason for their involvement.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c6b569289500958d49ac52a"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3a06230355c18000067",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c5530db7dbaccfe0e9d523a"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "And they're rumored to have a secret BattleMech cache in the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LorePeriphery],Periphery]], since they are regularly able to replenish their battlefield losses with new machines from an unknown source.\n\nSo, if both of you are correct, then we might have just hit jackpot here. This might be the location of their secret supply cache.\n",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 4,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c08cf80d7f09b25965bda64"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
