      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3a06230355c18000067",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c87d64140ef6bab073a0108"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Before you both continue, I'll add that I consider the Dragoons to be the lowest probable hypothesis for what we'll find on this world. The most likely one, is something she mentioned during her interrogation, 'here might be [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLuderitzDragon],dragons]]'. \n\nI thought it might be related to the mercenaries, until I remembered its original usage. On ancient [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTerra],Terra]] maps the cartographers would write that on unknown lands to warn travelers of possible dangers.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 6,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9cd58fed9bd9a1e2d7c20663"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c1b77bc1787a2aabb92d92f"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "I agree that the reference would point towards one of the edges of the Hyades Rim, and the specific mention of dragons only fits this system. \n\nBut even so, why would a pirate want us to go to this system when facing possible death? To recover her [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreLosTech],lostech]] treasure? She was clearly trying to bait us. What that pirate said cannot be trusted. Period.\n\n",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 7,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c92cab3cdada4340cbf0ced"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
