    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ce143f68924823467c62055"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "I see two possible target areas based on your navigational data, Sumire. \n\nPrevious sensor sweeps indicate that one of them is a military facility with active sensors, and the other one's status is unknown. If there's a cache, those look like the two locations where we should start looking.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 13,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c48e90c8d01350ddbe938fc"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "59b98a97623035ac140056c6",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cede2467f3fa2c4ba216e6e"
      },
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Can we avoid those bases, or do we want just to start looking in the non-obvious places? In [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTaurus],Taurus]] they have a saying, 'mess with the bull, get the horns'.\n\nAnd if there are guards, might I inquire whom do you think we'll be fighting exactly?",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 14,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c62ba729309c3070d6c9ce2"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
      "inputMaxLength": 0,
      "sourceTopicRef": null,
      "subjectTopicRefs": [],
      "sourceInSceneRef": null,
      "sourceWithTagInScene": "",
      "override_speaker": null,
      "speaker_override_id": "598cd3f36230355c1800006a",
      "actions": null,
      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c1b547c5f04dd5f45b8e244"
      },
      "index": 14,
      "text": "We don't know with what kind of forces we'll be dealing with, Kittens, [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreWolfsDragoons],Dragoons]], or just other pirates since this system is lawless. \n\nSo I agree that we need to figure out what's happening here exactly, and our best bet is take out that active base before we investigate that other site on the main planet's equatorial region. ",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 15,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c56842a9c08675cd92bc9d8"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
