      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cae802927e7248ef7c296fb"
      },
      "index": 17,
      "text": "After we deploy to the first site, we should be able to overfly the other area.\n\nThat's it, Commander. First we hit the pirate base on the equator, then we investigate the second site. If we're lucky we might find something worthwhile down there.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "Carry on, Darius.",
